==={{anchor|Event 9}} Event 9: $1,500 No Limit Hold'em Short Handed===

* '''3-Day Event:''' Wednesday, June 3 to Friday, June 5
* '''Number of buy-ins:''' 1,459
* '''Total prize pool:''' ${{nts|1991535}}
