{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}} {{Infobox cricketer | name = BB Pradhan | image = Afghanistan national cricket team.jpg | caption = Pradhan, the umpire in black on the left, in a match between [[Afghanistan national cricket team|Afghanistan]] and [[Ireland cricket team|Ireland]] in the [[2010 ICC World Cricket League Division One|2010 ICC WCL Division One]] | country = Nepal | fullname = Buddhi Bahadur Pradhan | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1975|12|15|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Biratnagar]], [[Nepal]] | death_date = | death_place = | batting = | role = [[Umpire (cricket)|Umpire]] | umpire = true | odisumpired = 26 | umpodidebutyr = 2006 | umpodilastyr = 2017 | t20isumpired = 21 | umpt20idebutyr = 2012 | umpt20ilastyr = 2017 | date = 8 December 2017 | source = http://www.espncricinfo.com/srilanka/content/player/208255.html ESPN Cricinfo }}
'''Buddhi Bahadhur Pradhan''' ({{lang-ne|बुद्धि प्रधान}}) (born 15 December 1978 in [[Biratnagar]], [[Nepal]]) is an international [[cricket]] [[Umpire (cricket)|umpire]].<ref name="Cricinfo">{{Cite web|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/208255.html |title=Buddhi Pradhan |accessdate=16 May 2014 |work=ESPN Cricinfo}}</ref> He has umpired 24 [[One Day International]]s<ref>{{cite web |subscription=yes |url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/48/48269/Umpire_in_One-Day_International_Matches.html|title=Buddhi Pradhan as Umpire in One-Day International Matches|publisher=CricketArchive|accessdate=25 August 2011}}</ref> and 16 [[Twenty20 International]] matches, all involving the [[ICC members#Associate Members|associate nations]].<ref>{{cite web |subscription=yes |url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/48/48269/Umpire_in_First-Class_Matches.html|title=Buddhi Pradhan as Umpire in First-Class Matches|publisher=CricketArchive|accessdate=25 August 2011}}</ref> He was the first umpire from [[Nepal]] to stand in a One Day International match.
In January 2018, he was named as one of the seventeen on-field umpires for the [[2018 Under-19 Cricket World Cup]].<ref name="2018U19">{{cite web |url=https://www.icc-cricket.com/media-releases/586590 |title=Match officials appointed for U19 Cricket World Cup |work=International Cricket Council |accessdate=4 January 2018}}</ref>
==See also== * [[List of One Day International cricket umpires]] * [[List of Twenty20 International cricket umpires]]
